CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 13, 1957, pg. 13 reads: "Daisy E. Lampkin Lauded for Service to Mankind At Colorful Testimonial in Webster Hall - Banquet Honoree Daisy Lampkin notable national figure, and William Lampkin, her husband, enjoy the testimonial given for her last week in Pittsburgh by a committee of 100 citizens...Master of Ceremonies, Atty. K. Leroy Irvis"
TitMainTitle: William Lampkin, honoree Daisy Lampkin, and Atty. K. Leroy Irvis, seated at banquet table in Webster Hall
